Developer Terms of Use
des: Alias Maker is a random name generator to give you a new identity in a hurry. Whether you need a new name for a night out on the town, a character in your next book, or to make your neighbors think you lead a double life, Alias Maker has you covered. Simply ask Alias Maker to give you a new name and one of hundreds of millions of combinations will be generated for you.
